title: MFA Press Statement: President Tony Tan Keng Yam’s State Visit to New Zealand, 25 to ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the Republic of Singapore ) President Tony Tan Keng Yam will make a State Visit to New Zealand from 25 - 30 October 2015 , at the invitation of New Zealand Governor-General Sir Jerry Mateparae .
